subSubSection.paragraph:
Floral micromorphological characters, achene surface feature, and chromosome number
:—The filament collar of the new species consists of uniformly sized cells (
Fig. 3A
), and the anther endothecial cell wall thickenings are polar (
Fig. 3B
). The achene is glabrous and smooth (
Fig. 3C
). The chromosome number is 2 
n
= 60 (
Fig. 3D
).
